 on. Or something like that. Keep kicking ass and being you. Sorry I don&#39;t have something more eloquent to say.</p><span id='bc_0_72MN' class='comment-actions secondary-text' kind='m'><a kind='i' href='javascript:;' target='_self' o='r'>Reply</a><span class='item-control blog-admin pid-989975516'><a o='d' target='_self' href='http://www.blogger.com/delete-comment.g?blogID=6389679439326917475&amp;postID=5589590110590846529'>Delete</a></span></span></div><div id='bc_0_72BR' class='comment-replies'></div><div id='bc_0_72B_box' class='comment-replybox-single'></div></li><li id='bc_0_73B' class='comment' kind='b'><div class='avatar-image-container'><img src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/anon36.png'></img></div><div id='c2554052722417404479' class='comment-block'><div id='bc_0_73M' class='comment-header' kind='m'><cite class='user'><a rel='nofollow' href='http://www.8bitdad.com'>Zach Rosenberg</a></cite><span class='icon user'></span><span class='datetime secondary-text'><a rel='nofollow' href='http://www.bloggerfather.com/2014/06/cancer.html?showComment=1401826465326&amp;m=1#c2554052722417404479'>June 3, 2014 at 4:14 PM</a></span></div><p id='bc_0_73MC' class='comment-content'>Continue to be yourself, Oren, because you are amazing.</p><span id='bc_0_73MN' class='comment-actions secondary-text' kind='m'><a kind='i' href='javascript:;' target='_self' o='r'>Reply</a><span class='item-control blog-admin pid-319486905'><a o='d' target='_self' href='http://www.blogger.com/delete-comment.g?blogID=6389679439326917475&amp;postID=2554052722417404479'>Delete</a></span></span></div><div id='bc_0_73BR' class='comment-replies'></div><div id='bc_0_73B_box' class='comment-replybox-single'></div></li><li id='bc_0_74B' class='comment' kind='b'><div class='avatar-image-container'><img src='http://img1.blogblog.com/img/anon36.png'></img></div><div id='c7530361951521273160' class='comment-block'><div id='bc_0_74M' class='comment-header' kind='m'><cite class='user'><a rel='nofollow' href=